data.description: GREAT DEAL on this rancher style home! Welcome to Southern Colorado!This stick built 3 bedroom 2 bath home has been updated with new wood flooring, remodeled kitchen with new heavy vinyl flooring, stainless steel appliances,  quartz kitchen countertops, new electric baseboard heat with thermostats, a pellet stove, and fresh paint. Additional highlights include a 1 car attached garage with work area, encapsulated vapor barrier in crawl space, large fenced back yard, and wood WC ramp. The property is close to the schools and situated on 4 city lots. Over 300 days of sunshine!
